org.jetel.graph.dictionary

Class SerializedDictionaryValue

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jetel.graph.dictionary.SerializedDictionaryValue

  • public class SerializedDictionaryValue
extends java.lang.Object
    Dictionary value in a simple "serialized" form. This form contains the dictionary key, type of the dictionary value, and the value represented as properties.
    Since:
    Apr 14, 2008
